1383af97d1?r=3D9p0gt ] for the excellent techbio overview and Dan [ https:/=
/substack.com/redirect/25e31a04-03c0-4b4c-80c5-7b8d99330b54?r=3D9p0gt ] for=
 editing! Subscribe to Elliot=E2=80=99s newsletter, The Century of Biology =
[ https://substack.com/redirect/38597133-906b-4871-a00a-318318e64245?r=3D9p=
0gt ], to stay up to date with the techbio revolution.
That=E2=80=99s all for today, we=E2=80=99ll see you Friday morning for a We=
ekly Dose of Optimism!
Thanks for reading,
Packy

