9p0gt" rel=3D"" style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">Flags=
hip</a><span>, which are all based in the Boston area. While there is varia=
bility in the mechanics between these types of funds, the core practice is =
the same: </span><strong>new companies are internally ideated, financed, an=
d incubated within the walls of VC funds.</strong></p><p style=3D"color: #1=
a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">There are tw=
o major challenges associated with this model:</p><ol style=3D"margin-top: =
0;"><li style=3D"margin-bottom: 4px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 0; mar=
