s partners saturate the number of board seats and operating roles that they=
 can reasonably hold. </span><strong>Simply put, this model doesn&#8217;t h=
ave the intrinsic network effects of the Silicon Valley tech ecosystem.</st=
rong></p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; ma=
rgin: 0 0 1em 0;"><span>The second crucial drawback is that scientists and =
